entries.s_16: An Imperial transport was shot down on Rori. Go investigate the crash site and recover what you can.
entries.s_20: Good, there's no time to lose. An Imperial transport was shot down on Rori. Go investigate the crash site and recover what you can.
entries.s_25: Waste no time. Do not let any of the important documents fall into Rebel hands.
entries.s_28: Well done. I do not impress easily. I don't expect the Rebels to think twice before shooting down another transport, but I will make sure they pay dearly whenever they do. Colonel Veers feels the same. You should speak with him.
entries.s_32: I've learned of a manufacturing shop where Rebel starships are being repaired. If we can find out where the ships are being delivered, we can tag them and track the starships to bigger Rebel bases or even to some of their larger ships.
entries.s_34: I've learned of a manufacturing shop where Rebel starships are being repaired. This is a golden opportunity.
entries.s_36: What do you need me to do?
entries.s_39: If we can find out where the ships are being delivered, we can tag them and track the starships to bigger Rebel bases or even to some of their larger ships.
entries.s_43: I'm afraid I only have orders I have are for those on active duty.
entries.s_44: The function of this base is not of your concern. I would suggest you make yourself scarce.
entries.s_46: I do not have any orders for you, trooper. I believe Lord Hethrir had sent for you.
